Opeyemi Falegan, ex-lover of popular actress, Nkechi Blessing Sunday, has spoken on what he’d do if the Labour Party standard bearer, Peter Obi wins the election. The politician whose affair with NBS ended in one of the worst ways ever promised to return to his ex if Obi clinches the seat of power. Read Also; Obi wins Edo with wide margin He wrote: “If Peter Obi enter, I go marry my ex (I get many ex o).